subject: Propaganda posters
text:
Here’s some propaganda posters for unhosted web apps, remotestorage
and Terms of Service; Didn’t Read:
https://github.com/unhosted/design/commit/5df258df57d46f3429caf7adcc3eb7b366e2ea36

It’s a hommage to the infamous »Home Taping Is Killing Music« campaign
against copyright infringement, which through the years already
spawned parodies like »Home Sewing Is Killing Fashion«. See
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Home_Taping_Is_Killing_Music

The typeface used is the openly licensed »Passion One«:
https://www.google.com/webfonts/specimen/Passion+One

-- 
www.tos-dr.info // www.twitter.com/tosdr // www.github.com/Unhosted/ToS-DR
